<title type="html"><![CDATA[Jamat Islami, Ikhwan al-Muslimin, Qutbis and Sururis • Criticisms Of The Methodology Of The Surrooreeyah – Shaykh Muhammad al-Wasaabee]]></title>

<category term="Jamat Islami, Ikhwan al-Muslimin, Qutbis and Sururis" scheme="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewforum.php?f=23" label="Jamat Islami, Ikhwan al-Muslimin, Qutbis and Sururis"/>
<content type="html" xml:base="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=947&amp;p=991#p991"><![CDATA[
<strong>Shaykh Muhammad al-Wasaabee</strong><br /><br /><em>Adaption: Taalib Alexander</em><br /><br />1. Muhammad Suroor who claimed – erroneously – that the books of creed (‘Aqeedah) are dry due them being only text from the Qur’aan and Sunnah;<br /><br />2. Muhammad Suroor who claimed – erroneously – that the scholars of Towheed are ‘slaves of slaves of slaves of the slave and their ultimate master is a Christian’ (i.e. George H. Bush);<br /><br />3. Muhammad Suroor who claimed – erroneously – that the scholars of Towheed are ‘liars’, ‘hypocrites’ and ‘spies’;<br /><br />4. Praise for the one – he is Hassan Turabi – who permits the Muslim to revert to Christianity or Judaism;<br /><br />5. Praise for the one – he is Hassan Turabi – who claims it is not permissible to say that Jews or Christians are not believers;<br /><br />6. Their praise of the one – he is Muhammad al-Ghazaalee – who makes fun of the hijab calling it a ‘tent’;<br /><br />7. Muhammad Suroor who claimed – erroneously – that ‘flags’ and ‘pictures of leaders’ are ‘false idols from the false idols of our age’;<br /><br />8. Muhammad Suroor – declared apostates those who commit a major sin;<br /><br />9. One of their senior ideologues accused the Committee of<br />Senior Scholars of Saudi Arabia of holding ‘Masonic ideology’;<br /><br />10. Their defense of the one who – erroneously – accused shaykh al-Albaanee of being a ‘secularist’ and ‘murji”;<br /><br />11. Their defence of the one – he is Sayyid Qutub – who erroneously criticised Prophet Moosa (Peace be upon him);<br /><br />12. Their defense of the one – he is Sayyid Qutub – who erroneously criticised the caliphate of the noble Companion ‘Uthmaan bin ‘Affaan (may Allaah be pleased with him);<br /><br />13. Their defense of the one – he is Sayyid Qutub – who erroneously accused some of the Companions of religious hypocrisy;<br /><br />14. Defense of the one – he is Sayyid Qutub – who erroneously stated that: ‘Islam is a mixture of socialism and Christianity’.<br /><br />15. Their defense of the one – he is Hassan al-Bannaa – who called to unity of the religions;<br /><br />16. Their praise of the one – he is Muhammad al-Ghazaalee – who calls to socialism and erroneously claims and that, ‘Islam is a socialist religion’.<br /><br />17. Their falsely accusing the People of the Sunnah of being ‘Khawaarij’, ‘Murji’ah’ or ‘Qadariyyah’;<br /><br />19. Their defense of the one – he is Muhammad al-Mas’ari – who said that Shaykh Abdul-Azeez bin Baaz (may Allaah have mercy upon him) had ‘reached a level of complete idiocy and senility.’<br /><br />20. Their defence of the one – al-Khomeini – who said, ‘the prophets did not succeed in their mission, and the ones who succeeded in that, they are our scholars’.<br /><br /><em>Source: Adapted from: 20 Criticisms of the Surooreeyah by Shaykh Muhammad al-Wasaabee(2006)</em><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=56">Shehzad Sattar</a> — Tue Jan 03, 2017 12:42 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
